results.description:
When this group of wayward teens found out each of their parents were criminal overlords, they set off running. Now the kids have discovered they each have unique abilities and talents and have stuck together to keep each other safe and do a little good in the world.
Looking for a book to bring in new readers, lapsed readers or curious readers? This is the one!
